    <!-- about me -->
    <h2 class="SectionTitle">Biography</h2>
    <div class="AboutMe" id="aboutme">
        <div class="MyPhoto"><img src="files/photo.jpg" title="Photo of Me" width="120" /></div>
        <div class="MyContent">
            <div id="mybio">
                I am a research scientist at Baidu Silicon Valley AI Lab (SVAIL). 
                Before that, I obtained my Ph.D in computer science at <nobr>UC Irvine</nobr> in 2016, under the supervision of Prof. <a href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~ihler/" target="blank">Alexander Ihler</a>. 
                Prior to UCI, I received my B.S. in computer science from Harbin Institute of Technology, and M.E. in software engineering from Tsinghua University.
            </div>
            <br />
            <div id="myemail">
                Email: <span id="emailaddress">weiping dot thu at gmail dot com</span>
